{"tid":451541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗戲院公司之外 連港鐵網上買直通車飛都要收手續費","createTime":"2017-10-29T10:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T04:57:11.000Z","uid":136994,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d268fb25e75bd25d0fc8c260bf9f568971f6e36a","tid":451541,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T10:27:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.it3.mtr.com.hk/b2c/frmFareGuangdong.asp?strLang=Big5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.it3.mtr.com.hk%2Fb2c%2FfrmFareGuangdong.asp%3FstrLang%3DBig5&d=NpjW283%2FYonYtd0K1zRA5v9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=f6896bb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.it3.mtr.com.hk/b2c/frmFareGuangdong.asp?strLang=Big5</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/29/182115_c24ed708e103f2a55744ffe5cdcee93d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F29%2F182115_c24ed708e103f2a55744ffe5cdcee93d.png&h=21f94f33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母狗鐵正一賤種<br />\n上網買張直通車飛居然要收一張飛$12手續費，<span style=\"color: red;\">係逐張飛計啊</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買一張小童飛個手續費就佔咗10-15%啦<br />\n反之，喺外國買greyhound等巴士車飛，上網advance買定一定比walk-in買平，walk-in分分鐘唔比你買<br />\n連港鐵呢啲大公司都咁撚抗拒電子付款，幫你地慳咗人手仲要向消費者收高額手續費，完全唔知醜字點寫<br />\n你哋班死仆街有乜資格講電子付款，e-commerce<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45308bb55cfc30a1a1c359d0b5c5f7cb51c896c4","tid":451541,"uid":136994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T10:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315937c5883f902a0a9adb3013db75d65785e83c","tid":451541,"uid":20867,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T10:50:28.000Z","msg":"你要去中國收陸路離境稅系好合理既事"},{"pid":"